\begin_inset Formula $u(0)=u(L)=0$
\end_inset

, and solved it in terms of the eigenfunctions of 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{d^{2}}{dx^{2}}$
\end_inset

 (giving a Fourier sine series).
 Here, we will consider a small variation on this:
